data.description: This very cool Frank Lloyd Wright - inspired home is nestled upon 2.5 wooded acres with beautiful mature trees,  a winding creek bed and is full of wildlife. While sitting on the large upper deck, expect to see deer frolicking on the hillside. This home is a reverse floor plan with the main bedrooms located in the lower level with private patio access. The main floor of the home has new carpeting throughout and is ready for all of your entertaining needs with two large living spaces full of windows connected by a massive two-sided gas fireplace. Don't miss the fun rustic shed out back waiting for it's next adventure...a great playhouse or super fun party barn! This secluded location is just minutes from Nashville and within close proximity to Bloomington. Enjoy on the weekends or year round!  This is a special property you won't want to miss! HVAC 2017, 40yr roof 2017
